{"product_id":"berrichi-age-defence-night-cream-refill-30ml","title":"BERRICHI Age Defence Night Cream REFILL 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eBerrichi night cream Night works for your skin while you rest. Rich and deeply hydrating, this night cream helps the skin to recover and recover from the day’s challenges, leaving it looking fresh and rested in the morning. It nourishes, hydrates and slows the signs of ageing, leaving skin more supple and plump.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBerrichi  Age Defence Night Cream:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNourishes and restores, making the skin stronger and more resistant\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSoothes irritated and inflamed skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDeep moisturizing effect that keeps the skin soft and supple\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEvens skin tone, reducing fine lines and wrinkles\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStimulates blood circulation, helping the skin to regenerate faster\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMain ingredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eFurcellaran \u003c\/span\u003e– antioxidant, helps to maintain skin moisture balance and strengthen the skin’s protective barrier, slows down the skin’s ageing process, reduces inflammation and dryness. Furtsellaran is obtained from algae grown in Estonian waters.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAstaxanthin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– an antioxidant, the most effective natural anti-ageing agent with the ability to penetrate cell membranes, affecting the skin deeply. Stimulates the production of collagen, balances the skin’s moisture levels, protects the skin from central irritants.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eRetinol\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– improves skin texture, increases radiance and acts against signs of aging. Retinol accelerates cell healing and skin renewal, increases collagen production, while smoothing out unevenness\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAloe Vera\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– antioxidant, antibacterial and anti-inflammatory properties that accelerate healing, moisturise the skin and prevent ageing.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCacay oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e– rich in vitamins A and E. Helps reduce wrinkles and improve skin elasticity, stimulating collagen production and cell renewal.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e Suitable for all skin types\u003c\/span\u003e. Recommended for age 25+\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to clean skin or apply serum. Use only as a night cream because it contains retinol. The effect of retinol is deactivated by the sun and can make the skin more sensitive to the sun.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Persea Gratissima oil (Organic Avocado oil), Prunus Armeniaca kernel oil (Organic Apricot kernel oil), Caryodendron Orinocense seed oil (Cacay oil), Aleurites Moluccana seed oil (Kukui nut oil), Cetearyl Olivate\/Sorbitan Olivate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Aloe Barbadensis leaf juice (Aloe Vera), Benzyl Alcohol\/Dehydroacetic Acid\/Sorbic Acid\/Benzoic Acid, Retinol\/ Adenosine\/Hydroxypropyl Cyclodextrin (Retinol A-vitamin), Furcellaria Lumbricalis extract (Furcellaran), Haematococcus pluvialis\/AstaZine (Astaxanthin oil)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFree from parabens, silicones, mineral oils, synthetic flavours and colourants. Cruelty free and vegan. Suitable for sensitive and allergic skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Berrichi","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51084294717767,"sku":null,"price":25.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/berrichi-age-defence-night-cream-refill-30ml-277446.png?v=1739979948","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/berrichi-age-defence-night-cream-refill-30ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}